      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37315581">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aihaivara/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3087969-2.jpg" alt="玉籬園泡茶" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37315581/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37315581/" class="">第26页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aihaivara/" class=" " title="玉籬園泡茶">玉籬園泡茶</a>
                (唯能極於情，故能極於劍。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37315581">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">授与动词可以细分为四类：
（1）授与（give）东西：give, afford, allow, strick, lend, send, forward, promise, make
（2）告知（tell）事情：tell, teach, show, want, sing, read
（3）贡献（render）服务：render, do
（4）施行（perform）恩惠（有关得失的）：get, gain, procure, win, lose

前三类中的间接宾语都可以加“to”改成介词片语，唯最后一类不能用“to”，要用表示目的的介词“for”来把间接宾语改写为介..</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-05 16:11</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                授与动词可以细分为四类：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>（1）授与（give）东西：give, afford, allow, strick, lend, send, forward, promise, make<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>（2）告知（tell）事情：tell, teach, show, want, sing, read<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>（3）贡献（render）服务：render, do<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>（4）施行（perform）恩惠（有关得失的）：get, gain, procure, win, lose<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>前三类中的间接宾语都可以加“to”改成介词片语，唯最后一类不能用“to”，要用表示目的的介词“for”来把间接宾语改写为介词片语。例：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Give me the book = Give the book to me<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Tell us a story = Tell a story to us<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Do me a favour = Do a favour to me<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Get me a glass of water = Get a glass of water for me<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>只有授与动词才能接用两个宾语（直接宾语和间接宾语），其他的他动词则只能接用一个宾语.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>变则的授与动词，只有间接宾语，无直接宾语：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Modesty becomes a young man.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>I am prepared for the worst that can befall me.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>This house cost me thirty thousand dollars.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>How long did it take you to master English.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>This coat has lasted me five years.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>My knowledge of English stood me in good stead.
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
