        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36809025/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36809025/" class="">第13页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aihaivara/" class=" " title="玉籬園泡茶">玉籬園泡茶</a>
                (唯能極於情，故能極於劍。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36809025">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">……英文的形容词，常可用“of + 名词”所构成的形容词片语来代替，如useful可用of use来代替，use-less可用of no use来代替，……</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-12-20 20:26</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>……英文的形容词，常可用“of + 名词”所构成的形容词片语来代替，如useful可用of use来代替，use-less可用of no use来代替，……</q></blockquote>
